Buck gets covid - or "whimpycron" as he puts it - and Clay questions when we'll ever get back to normal. Judicial Watch’s Tom Fitton on the Jan. 6th and Fauci probes. Ignoramus Stephen Colbert: Abolish the Senate. New Virginia AG Jason Miyares hits it out of the park!
